snippet.title: Arcade Game: Kamikaze Cabbie (1984 Data East)
snippet.description:
A Maze/Driving Game. 

A bootleg of this game is also called "Yellow Cab".

Note: The game is endless so I quit afterwards. Used Invincibility cheat via dipswitch setting after down to last life.
